{"thag2.48:0.1":"Theragatha 2.48 ","thag2.48:0.2":"Dukanipata ","thag2.48:0.3":"Pancamavagga ","thag2.48:0.4":"Vajjitattheragatha ","thag2.48:1.1":"“Samsaram dighamaddhanam, ","thag2.48:1.2":"gatisu parivattisam; ","thag2.48:1.3":"Apassam ariyasaccani, ","thag2.48:1.4":"andhabhuto puthujjano. ","thag2.48:2.1":"Tassa me appamattassa, ","thag2.48:2.2":"samsara vinalikata; ","thag2.48:2.3":"Sabba gati samucchinna, ","thag2.48:2.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo”ti. ","thag2.48:2.5":"… Vajjito thero …. "}